      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Hammad, from Al Halby who said, ",
          "‘The woman divorced by Al-<span class=\"iTxt\">Khul’a</span> is not to be provided for’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "3. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from ibn abu ‘Umayr from Hammad from al-Halabiy who has said the following: “He (the Imam) ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said that woman of al-Khul‘ does not receive any benefits.’” "
        ]
      }
